Rip Notes
=========
Most of the movie is pretty much motionless with people talking in a dark background barely moving a muscle. Our first pass turned out 435MB which means with a ~100MB MP3 we'd still have to fill 150MB with nothing good. Since it's quite a high res already it seemed silly not to use the space for AC3. DRF value is also an indication: 3.08 (DivX DRF Analyzer) or 3.62 (avinaptic). Subtitles were a bit weird on this one. The English in IDX is empty but it is available in closed captioning. Lots of other subtitles are available as well.

